hman AbdulRazaq has approved the conduct of 2019 promotion exercise for all state government workers, including serving deputy directors. This is contained in a press statement issued by his Chief Press Secretary, Rafiu Ajakaye to journalists in Ilorin on Wednesday. According… August 19, 2020 In "News" The Kwara State Civil Service Commission says it will conduct the 2016 promotion examination for civil servants progressing to Grade Level 17 from all Ministries, Departments and Agencies on Friday, Sept. 23. September 20, 2016 In "News"